        "title": "Harmful Responses",
        "message": "Responding with shock, disappointment, or judgment when a child shares their identity or harassment experiences can cause lasting harm. This type of reaction:\n\n- Deepens their feelings of isolation and shame\n- Damages trust in your relationship\n- Discourages them from coming to you with future problems\n- May contribute to mental health issues\n- Teaches them to hide their authentic self\n\nInstead, respond with compassion, support, and a focus on their wellbeing rather than your own feelings.",
